{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act18d0_level_act18d0_05_beg","storyGroup":"act18d0","storySort":8,"storyDependence":"act18d0_level_act18d0_st01","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"WD-5","storyName":"沁礁之地","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"回到现代，萨尔贡，慑砂和暴雨谨慎地对待着这位突然提出要加入罗德岛的神秘人“沙卒”。而他的真实身份，似乎与凯尔希有所牵连。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act18d0/level_act18d0_05_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act18d0_05","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":6,"next":8,"characters":["暴雨","“沙卒”","慑砂","罗德岛干员"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"4上","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Text","text":"现代","id":8},{"type":"Text","text":"3:32 P.M.  天气/晴","id":9},{"type":"Text","text":"萨尔贡中部，伊巴特地区，无名城镇","id":10},{"type":"Dialog","id":11},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":12},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_indoor4","screenadapt":"coverall","id":13},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":14},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":15},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"......你想跟我们走......？","id":17,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","id":18},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"你应该明白，对我们而言，你只是个可疑分子。","id":19,"figure":"char_304_hvrain"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"检查过你的队伍了吗？","id":21,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"2","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"暴雨？","id":23,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"......一切正常。","id":25,"figure":"char_304_hvrain"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"但我不信任你。","id":26,"figure":"char_304_hvrain"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"嗯嗯，说得好，我当然不值得信任。","id":28,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"你的目的是什么？","id":30,"figure":"char_304_hvrain"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"我的目的是......找到我的目的。","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"你在说什么——","id":34,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"你们知道吗？伊巴特地区的王酋——曾惨死在火灾之中。","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1","focus":"2","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"......那是两三年前的事了。现任王酋是他的儿子，在伊巴特地区引发了不小的骚动......","id":38,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"多亏了那场火，我还不得不重新找个老东家，多花几个月时间适应新工作，烦人得很。","id":39,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1","focus":"1","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"是啊，是啊，可那是我的最后一个猎物。","id":41,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"织好了网，铺好了陷阱，却没有猎物，我现在，很无所事事啊。","id":42,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#3","focus":"2","id":43},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"——","id":45,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#2","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#3","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"——你、你杀死了一位王酋......？","id":48,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#3","focus":"2","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"萨尔贡的军队会找上你——","id":50,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"——不，等等，你为什么要告诉我们！？","id":53,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"1","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"啊，不愧是黑市里的常客。是啊，除了你们和我，没有人知道王酋的死和我有关。","id":55,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"至于萨尔贡的军队嘛......今非昔比，统治伊巴特地区的帕夏，可完全瞧不上这片荒芜的土地。","id":56,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"我想，帕夏应该不会在乎是父亲还是儿子当领主吧，其实我也不是很在乎。","id":57,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"我只是索求他的死亡，很简单的要求。","id":58,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"你的目的到底是什么？","id":60,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#5","focus":"2","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"复仇。","id":62,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"这个答案太无趣了，所以我从来不会回答。也许这片大地上有一半的人类都有自己复仇的目标，对敌人，对城市，对这片大地，怎么都好。","id":63,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"二十多年过去了，我一直在做这一件事。","id":64,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"权力、地位、财富，这些都是附属品，如果有必要，丢掉就丢掉吧。","id":65,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#3","focus":"2","id":66},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"或者，我会全部赠送给，“罗德岛”。","id":67,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"这可是前所未有的酬宾了，不是吗？","id":68,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"......","id":70,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"呵，看来你还是不愿意信任我，谨慎的小姐，你以前是军人吗，萨尔贡的军人？","id":72,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"——与你无关。","id":74,"figure":"char_304_hvrain"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#2","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"你呢，年轻的“桥”？或者我该称呼你如今的名字，“慑砂”？","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#2","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"2","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"......","id":78,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"慑砂，他不值得信任。","id":80,"figure":"char_304_hvrain"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"2","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"......你隐瞒了某些很关键的事情吧？","id":82,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"1","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"唔？","id":84,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#6","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"哦......是了，是啊，我怎么把这都忘了......","id":86,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"你们自诩是一个治疗感染者的医疗公司......好吧，我就暂且相信这片大地上还有这么异想天开的一群人吧。","id":87,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"1","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"我是一名感染者。","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"我拥有足够匹敌王酋的财富，也拥有能够陷害一位王酋的人脉与实力。","id":90,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"1","id":91},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"我用这全部，交换一份治疗机会，怎么样？","id":92,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#2","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"——你疯了。","id":94,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#2","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#3","focus":"2","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"我常这么觉得。","id":96,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"但没有人是不想活命的。我抛弃这一切来寻求治疗，难道不合理吗？","id":97,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"2","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"不，我想暴雨不是在说这个。","id":99,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"2","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"你竟然连自己是感染者这件事，都毫不在意......？","id":101,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"那你到底想在罗德岛得到什么？","id":102,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#6","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"1","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"......","id":104,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"1","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"好吧，时间也不多了，让我们坦诚相待吧。","id":106,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"我要找“凯尔希”。","id":107,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"也许她会告诉我很多事情，也许她会为我指出一条出路......当然，更多的可能是，她都不会做，狡诈地，把选择权重新交给我。","id":108,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"但就算那样也可以。","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"在每一位参与当年事件的人都被我逐一清除干净后，我对萨尔贡再无依恋，我迫切地想要离开这块令人作呕的土地。","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"我需要一个新的开始。","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"正巧在这个节点上，谁会放过一个出现在自己面前的，过去的影子呢？","id":112,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"......凯尔希医生和你是什么关系？","id":114,"figure":"char_304_hvrain"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"啊哈......说来话长。","id":116,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"她是我的救命恩人。我很感谢她，发自肺腑。","id":117,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#3","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"决定权不在我们......","id":119,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"2","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"......三年前，伊巴特王酋在旅途中死于一场大火，那场大火烧光了整座城镇，之后，他的儿子掀起了叛乱，和其他人争夺王酋之位。","id":121,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"是你做的。","id":122,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"1","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"如我所说。","id":124,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#4","focus":"2","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"为什么？","id":126,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#4","focus":"1","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"喔，陈年往事罢了，我只是在本来就满是间隙的可悲亲情之间插入了一些小小的......楔子。","id":128,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"你为什么想要知道这个？","id":129,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"2","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"......我在找一条线索，拜你所赐，我不得不终止了在伊巴特地区的调查。","id":131,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"1","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"哦......线索。","id":133,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"也许这也可以成为你信任我的契机，说说看吧，但愿我能帮得上忙。","id":134,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"2","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"我在找一个人。一个哥伦比亚的军工实验负责人。","id":136,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"1","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"你在调查哥伦比亚的公司，为什么？","id":138,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"2","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"......因为我最尊敬的人死在了一场可笑的意外里。","id":140,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"1","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"如果那真的只是场意外？","id":142,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"2","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"那我也要......得知真相。何况这也不是那些人踩着我兄长的死往上升官的理由吧？","id":144,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"1","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"......慑砂。","id":146,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"2","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"我知道，这是我的个人问题了......但机会难得，是吧，“沙卒”。","id":148,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"1","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"呵呵，咳，失礼了。","id":150,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"我说什么来着？","id":151,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"几乎每个活着的人，都需要复仇，对象可大可小，执念可深可浅。复仇是人生的一个永恒的母题。","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"如果你们允许我前往罗德岛接受治疗，我可以为你调查这件事。当然，刚才说的所有交易依旧全部作数。","id":153,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"哪怕是门外那批货物的十倍数量，我都有渠道可以解决，而且价格低廉，手尾干净，于一家制药企业而言，这再划算不过了吧？","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"1","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"......慑砂，抱歉，你的个人诉求不能被算作筹码。","id":156,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"2","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"这我当然知道......我只是......","id":158,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"1","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"对了......我险些忘了，看来我最近很容易忘事。","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"那个老伊辛留下的预言，我从没当真过。但事到如今再去想想，也许预言其意，只是某种交涉和沟通。","id":161,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"呵，预言......血肉凡胎可做不到与时间平起平坐。哪有这么便利的源石技艺呢。","id":162,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#3","focus":"2","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"......预言？","id":164,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#3","focus":"1","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"可惜老伊辛已经不在了，罢了，希望她还记得这个约定吧。","id":166,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"她是否有......多交给你们一枚金币？","id":167,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"一枚萨尔贡的古老金币。","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#2","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"......！","id":170,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#2"},{"type":"dialog","id":171},{"type":"character","id":172},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.5","id":173},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":174},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"暴雨，慑砂，有情况。","id":176,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#5","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"......","id":178,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#3","focus":"2","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"别慌，咋了？","id":180,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#3","focus":"1","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"......有很多可疑的队伍，他们在靠近这座城镇。","id":182,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#5","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"提醒各位，来者不善。","id":184,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"呃，而且速度很快，如果现在要跑我们还来得及，再慢的话，就避不开交火了。","id":186,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"十五分钟，我们最多就剩十五分钟，队长，副队长，动作得快。","id":187,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#5","focus":"1","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"——是你的人？","id":189,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#3","focus":"2","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"怎么会呢，我如今可是孤家寡人了。人可没有机械值得信赖。","id":191,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"不过，他们大概都是冲着我来的。","id":192,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"2","id":193},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"——该死的，你算好的！","id":195,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"1","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"要么帮我逃走，要么咱们一起对付这些不知天高地厚的杀手。","id":197,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"如何？","id":198,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#3","focus":"1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"暴雨","text":"......","id":200,"figure":"char_304_hvrain#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_304_hvrain#4","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"我、我们要怎么办？","id":202,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"悉听尊便。","id":204,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"2","id":205},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"啧，你这家伙——","id":207,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"——最后一个问题，你为什么要烧了那座城镇？只是刺杀一个王酋，有必要把那么多人都卷进来吗？","id":209,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"2","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"你甚至还给了平民疏散的时间——你就是单纯要烧个镇子？赤角小镇离你的地盘有十万八千里吧？你到底想干什么——","id":211,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#5","focus":"1","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"目的很重要吗？","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"2","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"——为了确保你不是一个真的疯子或是战争狂什么的。","id":215,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"1","id":216},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"唔，有道理，但我想你不会明白的，我烧毁的只有过去。","id":217,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#4","focus":"2","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"还是你的复仇？","id":219,"figure":"char_379_sesa_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#4","focus":"1","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"不......","id":221,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_172_1#3","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"只是一场迟到的火葬。","id":223,"figure":"avg_npc_172_1#3"},{"type":"Dialog","id":224},{"type":"Character","id":225},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":226},{"type":"Image","id":227}],"characters":["暴雨","“沙卒”","慑砂","罗德岛干员"]}